The Makefile in this directory is generated by the Makefile in ../lib/

HOWTO:

h2xs -A -n snips
edit snips.xs
perl Makefile.PL
make

On Linux, shared library gives error about missing 'stat'. Need to add
-lc_nonshared in the Makefile.PL LIBS (at END, not at beginning of the
list of libraries).

FUNCTIONS
---------

scalar SV* newSVpv(char *, int)
scalar SV* newSVsc(SV *)

sv_setpv(SV*, char *)
sv_setsv(SV*. SV*)

hash HV* newHV();

hv_store(HV*, key, keylen, SV* value, 0)
hv_fetch(HV*, key, keylen, lval);
